# Platformer
Simple platformer implemented in Python and using the pygame libary.\
Just playing around...

## Installation and usage
- Create conda environment:
```
conda env create -f env.yml
```
- Activate conda environment:
```
conda activate game_env
```
- Play:
```
python game.py
```

